quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  73,20,"Pellet joom Ma na anndi haЙ—a juula ko Й“uri famЙ—ude e tataЙ“al jemma wollo feccere mammbo wondude e fedde e Й“een wonduЙ“e e Ma Alla hoddira jemma e Гұalawma O anndi on tonngataa mbo O yaafii mon, njannge ko newanii on e Quraana hombo anndi ma won e mon ГұawЙ“e goo ngona e Й—atngal ka leydi hoЙ“e ndaarta Й“ural Alla woЙ“Й“e kadi na kaЙ“ano laawol Alla njannge ko newanii mon e hembo ndarnon juulde tottiron askal Гұamlon Alla Гұamaande moЖҙЖҙere kala ko mbaЙ—aЙ—on ko*e mon e jam tawon mbo ka Alla hombo Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude e mawnude njobdi njaafnee Alla sabu Alla ko jaafatooЙ—o ko jurmotooЙ—o"
  74,1,Ko an yo mojiiЙ—o
  74,2,ЖҒaЕӢo waajo-Й—aa
  74,3,"Fii Joomi maa, mawninaa"
  74,4,"Comci maa Й—in, laЙ“Й“inaa"
  74,5,"Sanamuuji Й—in, woЙ—Й—ito-Й—aa"
  74,6,Wata a okkir fii heЙ“ugol ko Й“uri Й—um
  74,7,"Ko fii Joomi maa, muГұГұortaa"
  74,8,Si wuttaama ka allaandu
  74,9,"haray nden Гұalnde woni, Гұalaande sattunde"
  74,10,"e hoore heeferЙ“e Й“en, nde wanaa newiinde"
  74,11,Accidam e mo Mi tagi on kaГұun tun
  74,12,Mi waЙ—ani mo jawdi Й—uuЙ—undi
  74,13,e Й“iЙ—Й“e wonnduЙ“e e makko
  74,14,Mi yaГұГұani mo yaГұГұudee
  74,15,refti himo tamЖҙinoo nde mi Й“eydata
  74,16,ЖҠum waЙ—ataa ! Tawde o laatino sanndalЙ—iiЙ—o e Aayeeje Amen Й—en
  74,17,Aray Mi fawa mo lette sattuЙ—e
